lead_paragraph: American Marina Alex was "super happy" after finding herself in uncharted waters with the halfway lead at the Manulife LPGA Classic in Ontario on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Alex Shoots 64 for Second-Round Lead at Manulife LPGA Classic
